description.en: ChronoCoin will develop business enriching people's lives by converting the resources equally given on time to the visible value of point.ChronoCoin will promote businesses that are common languages that can be used in the economic zone and aim to revitalize the economy by improving sociality in the form of point granting, point granting authority, point reduction service in the form of points.It is a service that adds value in the form of ChronoPoint mainly to the time the user has been active, giving ChronoPoint according to the staying time such as the time lined up at shops and the time to eat To do. Once ChronoPoint has accumulated, it can be used for exchanging products and different stores. In addition, with the spread of smartphone applications, it is possible to check the user's action history and take marketing data. In addition, by providing aggregated market information to a consulting company and providing that information to stores, it is possible to connect customers with customers. You can do business in various ways, not just from general users. ChronoPoint is the most frequently used by other point issuers, but "time lapse from one year after last use" is "time lapse", but in Time Innovation, this ChronoPoint is used as ChronoCoin The industry first adopts a mechanism of redistributing according to the percentage of coin holdings. There are many cases where ICO buys coins only for speculative purpose of coin in recent years, but by adopting the method of redistribution of ChronoPoint (chrono point), it will be directly linked to 【expansion of business = reward】, ChronoCoin ( Chronocoin) The holder adopts the mechanism that can realize the real investment in the business.
